name: Urmia lake is dries up. #2
description: It was a lake , a greatest salt lake in iran and one of the beautiful lakes in all over the world. But unfortunately after water crisis in iran in recently years and built non-scientific dams on Zarrine-Rood and Simineh-Rood rivers this lake became dries up. Government has some plan for resuscitation of this wonderful lake. Flamingos are immigrants from here after this awful crisis and don’t comeback till now.
